# Changelog

Change logs for all versions.

[1.3.0] - 2024-10-10
### Added
- Added the task priority setting function
- Added the task classification function

### Fixed
- Fixed an issue where the task list was sorted incorrectly
- Fixed an issue where page refresh was not timely after deleting a task

### Improved
- Optimized task list loading speed
- Improved user interface responsiveness

[1.2.0] - 2024-9-25
### Added
- Added the task completion status marker function
- Added task reminder function

### Fixed
- Fixed the incomplete display of the task details page
- Fixed an issue where task editing failed to save

### Improved
- Optimized task creation process
- Improved the accuracy of task search function

[1.1.0] - 2024-09-25
### Added
- Added task search function
- Adds the task filtering function

### Fixed
- Fixed task list loading failure
- Fixed an issue where the mission details page style was misaligned

### Improved
- Optimized the display layout of the task list
- Improves the aesthetics of the user interface

[1.0.0] - 2023-09-15
### Added
- Initial release
- Implement basic task creation, editing, and deletion functions
- Add user registration and login functions

### Fixed
- Fixed several known issues in the initial release

### Improved
- Optimized user registration and login process
- Improves overall application stability and performance
